arStrings.szText: Look at this, these stone tablets contain some of the earliest written works of my druidic ancestors. All destroyed...

The wildlife in the Gaothmar Grasslands have been stirred into a frenzy recently. They've taken to smashing or even eating our runic tablets.
I don't blame the creatures, but we must preserve our history. As a fellow druid, I know you must agree. Please, retrieve whatever you can!
